name: KittehCoin
description: KittehCoin — the first cat in blockchain history, first launched in 2013 — has returned stronger than ever. Originally created as Dogecoin’s feline rival, KittehCoin pioneered cat-themed crypto before any other. Now rebuilt on BNB Chain, it’s back from our original domain kittehcoin.info and official X account @kittehcointeam, ready to reclaim its place in the crypto world with a growing community of true cat lovers.
